text: Santa Bárbara is a parish in the municipality of Angra do Heroísmo on the island of Terceira in the Azores. The population in 2011 was 1,274,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of .Eurostat It contains the localities As Nove, Canada da Nossa Senhora da Ajuda, Pico das Seis, Pico dos Enos and Santa Bárbara. ==References== Category:Parishes of Angra do Heroísmo
